The most-anticipated  game  of  the  year  and  the
sequel to the best-selling first-person action game
of  all  time,  Modern  Warfare  2  continues   the
gripping and heart-racing action  as  players  face
off against a new threat dedicated to bringing  the
world to the  brink  of  collapse.  Call  of  Duty:
Modern Warfare 2 features for  the  first  time  in
video games, the musical  soundtrack  of  legendary
Academy Award, Golden Globe Award, Grammy Award and
Tony winning composer Hans Zimmer. The title  picks
up immediately following  the  historic  events  of
Call of Duty 4:  Modern  Warfare,  the  blockbuster
title that earned worldwide critical acclaim.
